Zach Randolph的內容"},{"pid":"25ad91b6d39bf779abc9f83b6aa35cf0ec0364b5","tid":60510,"uid":5600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:21:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔陣間又擲玩具喊晒口話呢到唔是高登"}]}